### Show dotfiles

    CMD + SHIFT + .

### PostgreSQL

    $ brew install postgresql
    $ brew services start postgresql
    $ createdb `whoami`

### Brew

列出某个包安装的所有文件：

    $ brew list postgresql
    $ brew list -v postgresql

### Bash

    $ brew install bash
    $ brew install bash-completion@2
    $ brew install git
